subproject.corporate outcome: Enhanced national capacity to use ICT for development as driver for pro-poor capacity development and institutional building
subproject.description: a)Providing access to the appropriate IT technologies for M/SMEs. b) Developing IT-M/SME-business and local service providers in non-urban areas. c) Encouraging IT-M/SMEs to serve M/SMEs in non-urban areas. d) Improving IT capabilities of the M/SME service providers. e) Setting the standards for basic IT training for M/SMEs. f) Supporting the monitoring and performance measurement process
subproject.title: ICT for M/SMEs
